question: What is the successrate of medication Simvastatin 10 MG Oral Tablet?
answers:

    COUNT(CASE WHEN m.DESCRIPTION = 'Simvastatin 10 MG Oral Tablet' AND e.REASONCODE IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) / COUNT(CASE WHEN m.DESCRIPTION = 'Simvastatin 10 MG Oral Tablet' THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS success_rate
FROM 
    medications m
JOIN 
    encounters e ON m.ENCOUNTER = e.Id
WHERE

question: What is the successrate of medication NDA020800 0.3 ML Epinephrine 1 MG/ML Auto-Injector?
answers:
SELECT 
    (SUM(CASE WHEN medications.CODE = 'NDA020800' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN medications.CODE = 'NDA020800' AND medications.REASONCODE IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)) / 
    SUM(CASE WHEN medications.CODE = 'NDA020800' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS success_rate
FROM 
    medications 
JOIN 
    encounters ON medications.ENCOUNTER = encounters.Id 
JOIN 
    patients ON encounters.PATIENT = patients.Id 
WHERE 
    medications.CODE = 'NDA020800';

question: How many immunizations are uncovered by the payer with the ID 8fa6c185-e44e-3e34-8bd8-39be8694f4ce?
answers:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM immunizations
JOIN encounters ON immunizations.ENCOUNTER = encounters.Id
JOIN payers ON encounters.PAYER = payers.Id
WHERE payers.Id = '8fa6c185-e44e-3e34-8bd8-39be8694f4ce' AND immunizations.CODE NOT IN (
    SELECT medications.CODE
    FROM medications
    JOIN encounters ON medications.ENCOUNTER = encounters.Id
    WHERE encounters.PAYER = '8fa6c185-e44e-3e34-8bd8-39be8694f4ce'
);
